_header: With sorrow thou came into this world
_description: ‘Þis world is but a vanitee’ — twelve lines

BLRoy18Bxxiii.First Lines:
With sorowe þu com in to þis worldborne of þi moder
                    dere…
BLRoy18Bxxiii.Last Lines:
…to forsake synne or synne forsake þeI sey þe be god
                    almyght
